text: Gaskin may refer to: *Gaskin (surname) *9K31 Strela-1, a Russian military vehicle tagged with the NATO reporting name 'Gaskin' *Gaskin (horse) - large muscle on the hind leg of a horse or related animal between the stifle and the hock; the relevant section of the leg. Homologous to the human calf ==See also== *Gaskin v United Kingdom - European legal case
title: Gaskin
